          <p class="text-sm font-black text-pink-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">THE BEFORE</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">GlowBotanics, organic skincare brand in Los Angeles. Sold through Etsy only (product photos basic, ingredient list buried in product description, no shade finder, no subscription option). Monthly sales: $8,400 (120 units @ $70 average). Problem: "Customers ask same questions repeatedly: 'Is this really organic?' 'What shade matches my skin tone?' 'Can I subscribe for refill?' I spend 3 hours daily answering Etsy messages, losing sales to brands with professional sites. Beauty shoppers buy from brands they trust, not just pretty packaging."</p>
