          <p class="text-6xl font-black text-rose-700 mb-3">195%</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Sales Increase In 4 Months</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">$8,400/month (Etsy) â†’ $24,800/month (Shopify) in 4 months. Key drivers: Ingredient transparency (4x trust), shade quiz (67% higher conversion), subscriptions (73% retention).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TOOL COMPARISONS -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-50 to-rose-50">
